title: NineLAB | Community Stories | Science vs. Anti-Science: Vaccination with Claude Bernard, PhD
description:
Nine Network of Public Media offers digital story telling training to individuals and organizations to help them tell and share their stories of impact.

Community Producer Claire Anderson addresses the question of whether to vaccinate or not in this second installment of "Science vs. Anti-Science." Physicist, Claude Bernard, describes how to protect our children and our communities from dangerous childhood diseases, and talks about his own struggles with this issue when he was a new father.
